el | archivedate=August 2, 2014 | date=August 2, 2014 | accessdate=August 2, 2014 | work=Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre | language=Spanish | url-status=dead }}</ref>}}\n}}{{Professional wrestling title history middle\n|number =\u00a08\n|champion =\u00a0{{sortname|Matt|Taven}}\n|reign =\u00a01\n|date =\u00a0{{dts|2018|03|30}}\n|days =\u00a0{{age in days nts|month1=03|day1=30|year1=2018|month2=08|day2=03|year2=2018}}\n|location=[[Mexico City]]\n|event =\u00a0''[[CMLL Super Viernes|Super Viernes]]''\n|notes =\u00a0&nbsp;\n|ref =&nbsp;\n}}{{Professional wrestling title history middle\n|number =\u00a09\n|champion =\u00a0[[Volador Jr.]]\n|reign =\u00a03\n|date =\u00a0{{dts|2018|08|03}}\n|days =\u00a0{{age in days nts|month1=08|day1=03|year1=2018}}+\n|location=[[Mexico City]]\n|event =\u00a0[[Negro Casas 40th Anniversary Show]]\n|notes =\u00a0&nbsp;\n|ref =<ref name=Casas40Ovaciones>{{cite web | url=https://ovaciones.com/aceptan-el-reto/ | title=\u00a1Aceptan el reto! | first=Arturo | last=Rosas Plata | language=Spanish | date=August 4, 2018 | accessdate=September 21, 2018 | work=Ovaciones | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180923005724/https://ovaciones.com/aceptan-el-reto/ | archive-date=September 23, 2018 | url-status=dead }}</ref>\n}}\n{{BundleEnd}}\n\n==Combined reigns==\n[[File:LuchaLibreObrera153.JPG|thumb|[[Negro Casas]], the oldest wrestler to win the championship|alt=Mexican wrestler Negro Casas in the ring during an outdoor wrestling event.]]\n;Key\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n|style=\"background-color:#FFE6BD\"|\u2020\n|Indicates the current champion\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n! scope=\"col\" |Rank\n! scope=\"col\" |Wrestler\n! scope=\"col\" |No. of reigns\n! scope=\"col\" |Combined<br />days\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" |{{Tooltip|Ref(s).|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |1\n|style=\"background-color:#FFE6BD\"|[[Volador Jr.]] \u2020\n|3\n|{{age in days|month1=05|day1=20|year1=2014}}+\n|<ref name=VoladorJr2/><ref name=LaSombra2/><ref name=VoladorJr/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |2\n|{{sortname|Negro|Casas}}\n|1\n|475\n|<ref name=NegroCasas/><ref name=MascaraDorada/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |3\n|{{sortname|La|Sombra|La Sombra (wrestler)}}\n|2\n|393\n|<ref name=VoladorJr2/><ref name=LaSombra2/><ref name=LaSombra/><ref name=NegroCasas/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |4\n|[[Mephisto (wrestler)|Mephisto]]\n|1\n|213\n|<ref name=FirstHistoric/><ref name=LaSombra/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |5\n|{{sort|Mascara Dorada|[[M\u00e1scara Dorada]]}}\n|1\n|170\n|<ref name=MascaraDorada/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |6\n|{{sortname|Matt|Taven}}\n|1\n|126\n|\n|}\n\n{{clear}}\n\n==Footnotes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{refbegin}}\n*{{cite book|first1=Royal | last1=Duncan | first2=Gary | last2=Will | title=Wrestling title histories: professional wrestling champions around the world from the 19th century to the present | year=2000 | publisher=Archeus Communications | location=Waterloo, ON | isbn=0-9698161-5-4 | ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book | title=Legends of Pro Wrestling - 150 years of headlocks, body slams, and piledrivers | first=Tim | last=Hornbaker | publisher=Sports Publishing | isbn=978-1-61321-808-2 | location=New York, New York | chapter= Statistical notes | year= 2016 | edition=Revised | ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book | author= Madigan, Dan | title= Mondo Lucha a Go Go: the bizarre & honorable world of wild Mexican wrestling | publisher= HarperColins Publisher | year= 2007 | chapter = \"Okay... what is Lucha Libre?\" | page = 31 | quote=featuring clearly distinguished good guys and bad guys, or t\u00e9cnicos and rudos | isbn=978-0-06-085583-3|location=New York, New York| ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|last=Hornbaker | first=Tim|title= National Wrestling Alliance: the untold story of the monopoly that strangled pro wrestling|publisher=ECW Press|year=2007|chapter=International Expansion|isbn=978-1-55022-741-3| ref=harv}}\n{{refend}}\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n{{Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre championships}}\n{{NWA Worl